divs: Sighting DetailsOn Tuesday, August 13th as I was leaving for work, 3 military jets flew over & as I was looking up,jets were no longer visible, I noticed two white objects fly in opposite direction of the jets. My roommate was outside also so i asked him if he just saw the same thing, he did. One of the objects disappeared.
